      <title>日本批准向 Chip Venture Rapidus 提供 3.9B 美元补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-02/japan-approves-3-9b-in-aid-to-chip-venture-rapidus-video</link>
