      <title>香港引领亚洲股市走高，债券下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于香港股市在追赶交易中上涨，亚洲股市上涨，而在强劲的美国数据支持美联储将缓慢降息的观点后，该地区债券下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 21:58:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>外国人涌入印度债券引起市场轰动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/foreigners-flocking-to-indian-bonds-make-a-splash-across-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度被纳入主要全球债券指数的分水岭，大量资金涌入印度，正在重塑这个长期渴望免受热钱流入影响的国家的市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/foreigners-flocking-to-indian-bonds-make-a-splash-across-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 01:35:43 GMT</pubDate>
